{"word":"ἀγύρτης","slug":"ἀγύρτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγύρτης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγείρω'><el>ἀγείρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a collector</i>: <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>a begging priest</i> of Cybele, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>: then,<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a beggar, mountebank, vagabond, juggler</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}